msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F5</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Channel List for</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F5</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>विण्डो</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem></guimenuitem> कृते चैनलसूची"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a <link linkend=\"list-channels\">list of channels</link> available "
"on the server."
msgstr ""
"प्रदर्शयति क<link linkend=\"list-channels\"> चैनलानां सूची</link> सर्वरे उपलभ्यते।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Logfile for</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>विण्डो</guimenu> <guimenuitem></guimenuitem> कृते लॉगसञ्चिका "
"उद्घाटयन्तु"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a screen with the log of messages from the current tab. Only works "
"for <interface>Channel</interface>, <interface>Server Messages</interface>, "
"and <interface>Query</interface> tabs. Logging must be enabled in "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure "
"Konversation</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Behavior</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Logging</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main menu."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमान ट्याब् तः सन्देशानां लॉग् सहितं पटलं प्रदर्शयति । केवलं <interface>Channel</"
"interface>, <interface>Server Messages</interface>, <interface>Query</"
"interface> ट्याब् च कृते कार्यं करोति । मुख्यमेनूमध्ये <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>सेटिंग्स्</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>संवादं विन्यस्य</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>व्यवहारः</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>लॉगिंग्</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> इत्यत्र लॉगिंग् सक्षमं "
"भवितुमर्हति"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3169
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "सहायता मेनू"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konversation; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu item, for "
"more information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&संवादः; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तु, अधिकसूचनार्थं &kde; "
"मौलिकता।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "प्रश्नोत्तरम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When I start &konversation;, I'd like to connect to a server without joining "
"any channels. How do I do that?"
msgstr ""
"यदा अहं &konversation;, आरभ्णामि तदा अहं कस्यापि चैनल्-मध्ये सम्मिलितं विना सर्वरेण सह "
"सम्बद्धं कर्तुम् इच्छामि । तत् कथं करोमि ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <link linkend=\"serverlist-addnetwork\">Edit Server</link> screen, "
"leave the <guilabel>Channels</guilabel> frame empty."
msgstr ""
"इति<link linkend=\"serverlist-addnetwork\"> सर्वर सम्पादयतु</link> screen, "
"leave the<guilabel> चैनल्स्</guilabel> फ्रेम रिक्त।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3209
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konversation; won't connect to any servers. What is wrong?"
msgstr "&संवादः; कस्यापि सर्वरेण सह न सम्बद्धं भविष्यति। किं दोषः ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3212
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are several things that could be wrong."
msgstr "तत्र अनेकाः विषयाः सन्ति ये दोषपूर्णाः भवितुम् अर्हन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure that you have entered the correct <guilabel>Server name</guilabel> "
"and the correct <guilabel>Port</guilabel> in the <link linkend=\"serverlist-"
"addserver\">Add Server</link> screen."
msgstr ""
"भवन्तः सम्यक् प्रविष्टवन्तः इति सुनिश्चितं कुर्वन्तु<guilabel> सर्वर नाम</guilabel> सम्यक् "
"च<guilabel> पोताश्रय</guilabel> इति<link linkend=\"serverlist-addserver\"> "
"Server योजयतु</link> पट।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the output in the <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">Server "
"Messages</link> screen for any error messages. Did the server reject the "
"connection because of a bad password? Did the server reject the connection "
"because it requires <acronym>IDENTD</acronym> and your computer did not "
"respond to the <acronym>IDENT</acronym> request? Did you check the SSL "
"protocol box but the server does not support SSL?"
msgstr ""
"इत्यस्मिन् आउटपुट् पश्यन्तु<link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\"> सर्वर सन्देशाः</link> "
"कस्यापि त्रुटिसन्देशस्य कृते स्क्रीन् भवति। किं सर्वरेण दुष्टगुप्तशब्दस्य कारणेन संयोजनं अङ्गीकृतम्? "
"किं सर्वरेण <acronym>IDENTD इत्यस्य</acronym> आवश्यकता अस्ति इति कारणेन संयोजनं "
"अङ्गीकृतवान् तथा च भवतः सङ्गणकेन <acronym>IDENT</acronym> अनुरोधस्य प्रतिक्रिया न "
"दत्ता? किं भवान् SSL प्रोटोकॉलपेटिकां परीक्षितवान् परन्तु सर्वरः SSL समर्थयति न?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are behind a firewall, make sure the correct ports are enabled. "
"&konversation; needs the following ports enabled:"
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् अग्निप्रावरणस्य पृष्ठतः अस्ति तर्हि सम्यक् पोर्ट् सक्षमाः इति सुनिश्चितं कुर्वन्तु । "
"&संवादः; निम्नलिखित पोर्ट् सक्षमीकरणस्य आवश्यकता अस्ति:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Outgoing TCP 6667 (or the port of the server you connect to)"
msgstr "बहिर्गच्छन् TCP 6667 (अथवा यस्य सर्वरस्य पोर्ट् भवन्तः सम्बद्धाः सन्ति)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Incoming TCP 113 (if the server requires IDENTD)"
msgstr "आगच्छन् TCP 113 (यदि सर्वरस्य IDENTD आवश्यकम् अस्ति)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on &irc; connection problems, see <ulink url=\"https://"
"github.com/irchelp/wio/blob/gh-pages/networks/connectprob.md\">irchelp.org</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"अधिकविवरणार्थं &irc; संयोजनसमस्याः, <ulink url=\"https://github.com/irchelp/wio/"
"blob/gh-pages/networks/connectprob.md\">irchelp.org</ulink> इति पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When I go to <menuchoice> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Channel "
"List</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>, I cannot select it. Why is that?"
msgstr ""
"यदा अहं <menuchoice> <guimenu>विण्डो</guimenu> <guisubmenu>चैनलसूची</guisubmenu> "
"</menuchoice> इति गच्छामि तदा अहं तत् चिन्वितुं न शक्नोमि । तत् किमर्थम् ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Channel List</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> menu entry will be grayed-out if a non-channel "
"tab, &eg; <guilabel>Watched Nicks</guilabel>, is currently being viewed. To "
"make it selectable again go back to a channel tab or the server tab."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>विण्डो</guimenu> <guisubmenu>चैनलसूची</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> मेन्यूप्रविष्टिः ग्रे-आउट् भविष्यति यदि गैर-चैनल-ट्याब्, &eg; "
"<guilabel>Watched Nicks</guilabel>, सम्प्रति दृश्यते । पुनः चयनीयं कर्तुं पुनः चैनल् ट्याब् "
"अथवा सर्वर ट्याब् प्रति गच्छन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How do I have &konversation; automatically mark me as away after a period of "
"inactivity?"
msgstr "कथं मम &konversation; स्वयमेव निष्क्रियतायाः अवधिपश्चात् दूरं इति चिह्नितव्यम्?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Auto-away messages are configured on a per-identity basis. To enable auto-"
"away select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Identities</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Choose the identity for which you want to enable "
"auto-away from the drop down list at the top of the dialog and go to the "
"<guilabel>Away</guilabel> tab. Check the <guilabel>Automatic Away</guilabel> "
"option."
msgstr ""
"स्वतः-दूर-सन्देशाः प्रति-परिचय-आधारेण विन्यस्ताः भवन्ति । स्वतः दूरं सक्षमं कर्तुं "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>परिचयः</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> इति चिनोतु । यस्य परिचयस्य कृते भवान् संवादस्य उपरि ड्रॉप् डाउन सूचीतः स्वतः "
"दूरं सक्षमं कर्तुम् इच्छति तत् चित्वा <guilabel>दूर</guilabel> ट्याब् प्रति गच्छतु । "
"<guilabel>स्वचालितं दूरं</guilabel> विकल्पं पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How to avoid the <guilabel>Auto Replace</guilabel> feature of the "
"<interface>Input Line</interface>?"
msgstr ""
"<interface>Input Line</interface> इत्यस्य <guilabel>Auto Replace</guilabel> "
"इति विशेषतां कथं परिहर्तव्यम्?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo> instead of just "
"&Enter; to avoid parsing and automatically replacing the text in the "
"<interface>Input Line</interface> according to the options in the settings "
"dialog page <menuchoice><guimenu>Behavior</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Auto "
"Replace</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"केवलं &Enter; सेटिंग्स् संवादपृष्ठे विकल्पानुसारं <interface>Input Line</interface> "
"इत्यस्मिन् पाठस्य विश्लेषणं कृत्वा स्वयमेव प्रतिस्थापनं परिहरितुं "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>व्यवहारः</guimenu> <guimenuitem>स्वयं प्रतिस्थापनं</"
"guimenuitem></ मेनूचयन>।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Where can I find the scripts included with &konversation;?"
msgstr "&konversation; इत्यनेन सह समाविष्टानि स्क्रिप्ट् कुत्र प्राप्नुयाम्?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Run this command in &konversation;'s input line (using the media script as "
"an example, since it comes with any &konversation; installation):"
msgstr ""
"&konversation; इत्यस्य निवेशपङ्क्तौ एतत् आदेशं चालयन्तु (मीडिया स्क्रिप्ट् उदाहरणरूपेण "
"उपयुज्य, यतः एतत् कस्यापि &konversation; संस्थापनेन सह आगच्छति):"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:3298
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>--showpath media</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>--प्रदर्शनमार्गमाध्यम</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sample output: <replaceable>The script file 'media' was found at: /usr/share/"
"konversation/scripts/media</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"नमूनानिर्गमः : <replaceable>स्क्रिप्टसञ्चिका 'media' अत्र प्राप्ता: /usr/share/"
"konversation/scripts/media</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3305
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I make my text bold/italicized/underlined?"
msgstr "मम पाठं कथं गाढं/इटालिकं/अधोरेखाकृतं करोमि?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <userinput>This is my %Bbold%B text.</userinput>"
msgstr "उदाहरणम् : <userinput>इदं मम %Bbold%B पाठः ।</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3309 index.docbook:3315 index.docbook:3321 index.docbook:3327
#: index.docbook:3333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output:"
msgstr "उत्पादनम् :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3314
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <userinput>This is my %Iitalicized%I text.</userinput>"
msgstr "उदाहरणम् : <userinput>एषः मम %Iitalicized%I पाठः अस्ति ।</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <userinput>This is my %Uunderlined%U text.</userinput>"
msgstr "उदाहरणम् : <userinput>इदं मम %Uunderlined%U पाठः अस्ति ।</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3326
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <userinput>This is my %Sstruck-out%S text.</userinput>"
msgstr "उदाहरणम् : <userinput>इदं मम %Sstruck-out%S पाठः अस्ति ।</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3332
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <userinput>This is my %Mmonospace%M text.</userinput>"
msgstr "उदाहरणम् : <userinput>इदं मम %Mmonospace%M पाठः अस्ति ।</userinput>"

